mixin topic-card(type, topic, image)
  .main__card
    .main__card-img
      img.main__card-picture(src=image alt="изображение")
    .main__card-type= type 
    .main__card-topic= topic 
    .main__card-user
      span.main__card-author Niek Bove
      span.main__card-date April 3, 2018
      span.main__card-views 3k Views 
    .main__card-description If someone paid me, there would be ads here. However, no one paid me (sadly), so you won't see ads here. There could have been some lorem ipsum here, but I decided to share my thoughts with you, after all, this is kind of a post text. That's all.
      
